VariableName: Net state domestic product ( nsdp ) at factor cost for the base year 2011-12
Long_Description: Net State Domestic Product ( NSDP ) at factor cost in crore, the base year 2011-12. Data for the period 1985-86 to 2010-11 relate to NSDP at factor cost. The data prior to base year : 2011-12 relate to NSDP at factor cost.
